                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                        <span class="project-icon bg-primary text-white me-3">
                                            <i class="bi bi-cpu"></i>
                                        </span>
                                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Hybrid CNN-Transformer for CFD Simulations</h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="card-text">
                                        Developed a deep learning model combining CNN and transformer architectures to accelerate 
