                                    </p>
                                    <div class="mt-3">
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">PyTorch</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Deep Learning</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">CFD</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Transformers</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Insurance Dashboard -->
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                        <span class="project-icon bg-primary text-white me-3">
                                            <i class="bi bi-graph-up"></i>
                                        </span>
                                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Insurance Analytics Dashboard</h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="card-text">
                                        Built a comprehensive analytics dashboard for insurance data using .NET/Blazor, featuring 
                                        real-time data visualization, predictive analytics for risk assessment, and secure user 
                                        management. Implemented responsive design with Bootstrap for optimal UX.
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="mt-3">
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">.NET</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Blazor</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">C#</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Data Visualization</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Vector Database for AI Documentation -->
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                        <span class="project-icon bg-primary text-white me-3">
                                            <i class="bi bi-robot"></i>
                                        </span>
                                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Context-Aware GPT Documentation Assistant</h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="card-text">
                                        Created a vector database-powered documentation chatbot system that improved information 
                                        retrieval accuracy by 40%. Implemented embedding generation pipeline and semantic search 
                                        capabilities to provide context-aware responses for scientific instrument documentation.
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="mt-3">
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Vector Databases</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">OpenAI</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Azure</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Python</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- ML Workflow for Scientific Instruments -->
                        <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                        <span class="project-icon bg-primary text-white me-3">
                                            <i class="bi bi-gear"></i>
                                        </span>
                                        <h5 class="card-title mb-0">ML Workflow for Light Diffraction Analysis</h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="card-text">
                                        Designed and implemented an end-to-end ML pipeline for analyzing light diffraction patterns 
                                        in scientific instruments. Deployed on Azure ML with Kubernetes, the system processes 
                                        terabytes of spectral data to extract particle size distributions with 99.2% reliability.
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="mt-3">
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Azure ML</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Kubernetes</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Python</span>
                                        <span class="badge bg-primary me-1">Scientific Computing</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        }
        else if (section == "achievements")
        {
            <!-- Achievements & Impact Section -->
            <section id="achievements" class="py-5 section-alt-bg">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row mb-4">
                        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
                            <h2 class="section-title mb-3">Achievements & Impact</h2>
                            <div class="section-divider mb-4"></div>
                            <p class="lead">Measurable results and contributions that demonstrate my value</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
                            <!-- Achievement 1: Scientific Instrument Automation -->
                            <div class="achievement-card">
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                    <div class="achievement-icon">
                                        <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="ms-3">
                                        <h3 class="achievement-title">Scientific Data Analysis Automation</h3>
                                        <p class="achievement-description text-muted">Malvern Panalytical</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <p>Built ML workflows that <strong>reduced scientific data processing time from hours to seconds</strong>, 
                                enabling real-time analysis of complex diffraction patterns. Solution is now used by <strong>50+ scientists 
                                organization-wide</strong>, saving an estimated <strong>500+ research hours per month</strong>.</p>
                                <div class="stats-container mt-4">
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">98%</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Analysis Accuracy</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Hours Saved Monthly</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Active Users</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- Achievement 2: Vector Database for Documentation -->
                            <div class="achievement-card">
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                    <div class="achievement-icon">
                                        <i class="bi bi-robot"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="ms-3">
                                        <h3 class="achievement-title">Vector Database-Powered AI Assistant</h3>
                                        <p class="achievement-description text-muted">Industry Project</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
