                                <strong>improved query accuracy by 78%</strong> for technical documentation. The system 
                                <strong>reduced research time for scientists by 15 hours per week</strong> and is now deployed 
                                to production serving multiple departments.</p>
                                <div class="stats-container mt-4">
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">78%</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Accuracy Improvement</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">15h</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Weekly Time Saved</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">3</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Departments Served</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- Achievement 3: Azure ML & Kubernetes Deployment -->
                            <div class="achievement-card">
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                    <div class="achievement-icon">
                                        <i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-up"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="ms-3">
                                        <h3 class="achievement-title">Azure ML with Kubernetes Deployment</h3>
                                        <p class="achievement-description text-muted">Cross-Functional Project</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <p>Led deployment of machine learning models to Azure Kubernetes Service that 
                                <strong>scaled to handle 10,000+ requests daily with 99.9% uptime</strong>. Implemented a CI/CD pipeline 
                                that <strong>reduced model deployment time from days to under an hour</strong>, enabling faster 
                                iteration and delivery of new features.</p>
                                <div class="stats-container mt-4">
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">99.9%</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Service Uptime</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">10k+</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Daily Requests</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">95%</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Deployment Time Reduction</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- Achievement 4: Cross-Disciplinary Communication -->
                            <div class="achievement-card">
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3">
                                    <div class="achievement-icon">
                                        <i class="bi bi-people"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="ms-3">
                                        <h3 class="achievement-title">Cross-Disciplinary Team Leadership</h3>
                                        <p class="achievement-description text-muted">Team Collaboration</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <p>Successfully bridged communication between technical and domain expert teams (physicists, chemists, engineers), 
                                leading to <strong>three successful project implementations delivered on time and under budget</strong>. 
                                Recognized by management for exceptional ability to translate complex requirements into working 
                                technical solutions that met business needs.</p>
                                <div class="stats-container mt-4">
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">3</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">Major Projects Delivered</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="stat-card">
                                        <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
                                        <div class="stat-title">On-Time Delivery</div>
